lead_paragraph: The Tribune Broadcasting Company has agreed to swap two of its California radio stations with the Henry Broadcasting Company for Henry's Denver station and an undisclosed amount of cash. "This fits in with Tribune's local market development strategy," said Dennis J. FitzSimons, executive vice president of Tribune Broadcasting.
